pp3: This Privacy Policy is using in our app. Here's what you need to know:
pp4: 1. Information Collection: We do not collect any personal data from our users. The app operates solely in a simulated environment for educational purposes, and no real financial transactions or investments are involved.
pp5: 2. Coins Data: Quantum AI may access real-time cryptocurrency data to provide up-to-date information for educational purposes only. However, this data is not linked to any user's personal identity.
pp6: 3. Data Storage: Any virtual portfolio and associated data you create within the app are stored locally on your device and are not transmitted or shared with us or any third parties.
pp7: 4. In-App Advertising: Quantum AI does not display third-party advertisements to users.
pp8: 5. Data Security: We take reasonable precautions to safeguard any information you provide within the app. However, as the app does not collect personal data, your privacy is inherently protected.
pp9: 6. Age Restriction: Quantum AI is intended for 18+ ages Users.
pp10: By using Quantum AI, you agree to abide by this privacy policy. Please remember that this app is purely for educational purposes, and no real financial activities are involved.
pp11: For any questions or concerns about this privacy policy or the app, please contact us at (kttjdt@gmail.com).
